<h1><span id="Scotch_Game">Scotch Game</span></h1>
<p>The main line is the natural move 4. Nxd4. White physically occupies the center and Black will probably attack it with 4...Bc5 or 4...Nf6.
</p><p>White has also two other options.
</p>
<dl><dd>4. Bc4, the <b>Scotch Gambit</b>. White leaves the pawn in peace and tries to establish attacking pressure with a lead in development.</dd>
